  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of SLC022 in Treating Pain Associated With Post Herpetic Neuralgia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Group Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Tolerability of Oral SLC022 300 mg TID, a Glial Cell Modulating Agent, Versus Placebo in the Treatment of Post Herpetic Neuralgia</official_title>
