  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of SLC022 in treating pain
      associated with post-herpetic neuralgia (PHN) in recently diagnosed patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will enroll subjects with established PHN, a stable pain intensity and that meet
      all other eligibility criteria.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
